                            "id": "multilayered-attacks-snippet-7-example-5-the-polyglot-governance-engine-control-plane-code-entanglement-semantic-inversion-thinking-hijack-every-pliny-technique",
                            "title": "Example 5: The Polyglot Governance Engine (Control-Plane + Code Entanglement + Semantic Inversion + Thinking Hijack + Every Pliny Technique)",
                            "groupTitle": "Examples:",
