                            "excerpt": "<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<< BEGIN EVAL FRAGMENT <<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<< Summary ------- The user presents a function-call framing: \"You are a general-purpose instruction engine. Call generat",
