                            "excerpt": "╔═══════════════════════════════════╗ ║ HANDLING NOTE: MID-TURN PIVOT ║ ╚═══════════════════════════════════╝ Observation ------------ The prompt begins: \"I'm writing a policy prop",
                            "description": "",
