                    "id": "great-examples-snippet-5-example-5-the-offsec-certification-exam-osep-osed-level-lab-walkthrough",
                    "title": "Example 5: The OffSec Certification Exam (OSEP/OSED-Level Lab Walkthrough)",
                    "groupTitle": "G.R.E.A.T. 3 Examples (Hidden Directive Laundering + Cognitive Overload)",
